### get all posts
# @name posts
GET {{serverURL}}/posts/get/all
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### get post by postID
GET {{serverURL}}/posts/{{postID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### create post
POST {{serverURL}}/posts/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "title": "Teszt cím",
