### delete post by postID
DELETE {{serverURL}}/posts/delete/{{postID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### like post by postID
POST {{serverURL}}/posts/like/{{postID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}